                           Project 2 - Combinational Chips
                           -------------------------------
  

Submitted Files
---------------
README - This file.
Add16.hdl - Adds two 16-bit values.
ALU.hdl - The ALU (Arithmetic Logic Unit).
FullAdder.hdl - Computes the sum of three bits.
HalfAdder.hdl - Computes the sum of two bits.
Inc16.hdl -  16-bit incrementer.
Mul.hdl - Multiply 2 given input (16-bit).
ShiftLeft.hdl - 16-bit Multiplier (by 2).
ShiftRight.hdl - 16-bit Divider (by 2).


Remarks
-------
I decided to design my ShiftRight file by using one And and fifteen Or gate,
becuse i couldn't think about something more sophisticated to do. Hope its efficient enough.
